c^{-1}$ level.\nComparison with other measures of the transparency is provided; no other\nmeasure in the visible is as free of astrophysical assumptions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Oct 2008 20:00:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 3 May 2009 12:24:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-02-11"}
